data.description: This home offers so much for the next owner to call home. Inside you'll find a cozy family room with a vaulted and beamed ceiling that adds loads of charm and character. The main floor has the primary bedroom with direct access to the main floor bathroom. There is an additional area that could be used as a dedicated office, or a second main level bedroom.  Upstairs you will find two additional bedrooms that are large in size and a second full bathroom. Outside features a low maintenance yard and a 35X23 three stall garage. Come make this home yours today before it belongs to someone else!
